{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781721573541,"sessionID":"ses_12921062affexCJs9FOrxxcmSp","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_97dc1def084d48b398c85874","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Dashboard\n\n## Status\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Iterations completed | 1 / 1 (maxIterations) |\n| Verdict | **PASS** |\n| Release Readiness | in-progress |\n| Stop reason | maxIterations reached |\n\n## Severity Counts\n\n| Severity | Count |\n|----------|-------|\n| P0 | 0 |\n| P1 | 0 |\n| P2 | 2 |\n\n## Dimension Coverage\n\n| Dimension | Status | Iteration |\n|-----------|--------|-----------|\n| Correctness | covered | 1 |\n| Security | not covered | - |\n| Traceability | not covered | - |\n| Maintainability | not covered | - |\n\n## Findings\n\n| ID | Severity | Category | File | Summary |\n|----|----------|----------|------|---------|\n| P2-001 | P2 | correctness | maintenance-marker.ts:60 | activeLabels accumulates duplicate entries |\n| P2-002 | P2 | correctness | maintenance-marker.ts:73 | Label removal precedes activeCount decrement |\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-mimo-2/deep-review-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-mimo-2/deep-review-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-mimo-2/deep-review-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781721573535,"end":1781721573539}},"id":"prt_ed6e1a89c0015tgElIivkIUrfc","sessionID":"ses_12921062affexCJs9FOrxxcmSp","messageID":"msg_ed6e0f3c4001jH7P37H1Lq1WrJ"}}
